			<album>Hurrian Hymns</album>
			<trackNum>1</trackNum>
			<annotation>The song is dated to about 1400 BC, but VLC won&#39;t let me write a date with negative numbers, more than 4 digits, or letters, so I defaulted to 0000. I also got a GIF (non-animated) file to work as the preview for this album. This is the oldest known song in the world and comes from the Ancient Hurrian people.</annotation>
